---
import UseCase from '../../../UseCase.astro';
import UseCaseInteractive from '../../../UseCaseInteractive.astro';
import Usage from '../../../Usage.astro';
import UsageItem from '../../../UsageItem.astro';
---

<UseCase
  title="Feedback Loops Between Humans and AI"
  description="Use human corrections, edits, and preferences to improve future AI behaviorâ€”create a cycle where human input makes the AI better over time."
>
  <UseCaseInteractive clsHeight={112} label="Feedback loops" toggle>
    <div class="grid gap-600 w-full">
      <div class="grid gap-400 p-600 rounded-lg bg-tone-neutral-09 border border-tone-neutral-03">
        <div class="grid gap-200">
          <mds-text typography="label"><b>Learning from Edits</b></mds-text>
          <mds-text typography="body"
            >You edited "Monday" to "Tuesday" in this context. We'll remember this preference for
            similar meetings. [Learn more about how we use feedback]</mds-text
          >
          <mds-text typography="caption" class="text-tone-neutral-05"
            >The system acknowledges edits and explains how they improve future suggestions.</mds-text
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-400 p-600 rounded-lg bg-tone-neutral-09 border border-tone-neutral-03">
        <div class="grid gap-200">
          <mds-text typography="label"><b>Visible Improvement</b></mds-text>
          <mds-text typography="body"
            >Based on your previous edits, we've adjusted our suggestions. [See what changed] [Reset
            preferences]</mds-text
          >
          <mds-text typography="caption" class="text-tone-neutral-05"
            >Users see that their feedback is being used and can review or reset if needed.</mds-text
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-400 p-600 rounded-lg bg-status-error-10 border border-status-error-03">
        <div class="grid gap-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-200">
            <mds-icon name="mi/outline/error" class="text-status-error-05"></mds-icon>
            <mds-text typography="label"><b>No Feedback Loop (Problematic)</b></mds-text>
          </div>
          <mds-text typography="body"
            >Users repeatedly edit the same things (e.g. always changing "Monday" to "Tuesday"), but
            the AI keeps suggesting "Monday" every time. No indication that edits are used to
            improve suggestions.</mds-text
          >
          <mds-text typography="caption" class="text-status-error-06"
            >Frustrating repetition; users feel their input is ignored; the AI doesn't improve with
            use.</mds-text
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </UseCaseInteractive>
  <Usage>
    <UsageItem variant="do">
      Use human edits and corrections to improve future AI suggestions; acknowledge when feedback is
      being used.
    </UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="dont">
      Ignore repeated user corrections or make no visible use of feedback to improve suggestions.
    </UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="do">
      Show users how their feedback improved the system and let them review or reset learned
      preferences.
    </UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="dont">
      Learn from feedback invisibly without showing users that their input matters or how it's used.
    </UsageItem>
  </Usage>
</UseCase>
